# Cartcrft SPA fallback rules
# Processed by Netlify and Cloudflare Pages (and compatible hosts).
#
# The whole site is now a single client-rendered Vite + React SPA. Every route
# — marketing (/, /compare, /pricing, /legal/*), docs (/quickstart, /acp, …),
# the merchant dashboard (/dashboard/*), and the operator console
# (/superadmin/*) — is resolved by React Router in the browser. So ANY path
# must serve the one SPA shell (index.html); the zone router in src/Root.tsx
# then mounts the correct sub-app from the URL.
#
# Without a catch-all rewrite, a hard refresh or direct deep link returns 404.
#
# Format: source  destination  HTTP-status
#   200 = "serve destination content without redirecting" (rewrite, not redirect)

/*  /index.html  200
